  "takeaways": [
    "This audit checks whether the ROW Treasury leg behaves like a clean external deposit counterpart or a broader external-asset / nontransaction support channel.",
    "Quarter by quarter, the ROW Treasury leg is not a simple same-quarter liability counterpart: corr with `foreign_nonts_qoq` \u2248 -0.17, corr with `checkable_rest_of_world_bank_qoq` \u2248 0.02.",
    "At h0, the baseline TDC shock loads positively on the ROW Treasury leg and broader external support variables: ROW \u2248 11.76, foreign NONTS \u2248 26.59, foreign-bank interbank assets \u2248 5.00.",
    "The direct ROW bank-deposit-liability response is comparatively small at h0: checkable ROW deposits \u2248 0.22."
  ]
